&lt;li&gt;a clear and concise communicator (in written and verbal forms), who can distill the key risks and explain complex, nuanced issues in plain and simple terms;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a natural collaborator, able to guide cross-functional teams and drive to a win-win solution;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;familiar with the range of legal issues and commercial risks that arise in connection with hosted data and technology services; and&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;a team player who is willing to do what it takes to contribute to the collective success;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
