&lt;p&gt;The ML Platform team builds the platforms and services that enable ML engineers and data scientists across Stripe to take the data and build features and models from prototype to production — reliably, at low latency, and at scale. We work closely with product teams, data scientists, and platform infrastructure teams to build powerful, flexible, and user-friendly systems that substantially increase ML velocity across the company.&lt;/p&gt;
