&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a highly analytical, strategic, and execution-oriented individual to join the Stripe Finance &amp;amp; Strategy team, who will be embedded with Bridge as an early member of their small and fast-moving data &amp;amp; finance team. This role blends data, financial analysis &amp;amp; strategy, and plays a key role in defining, measuring and forecasting the financial and operational metrics that drive Bridge’s growth. You’ll work cross-functionally with Bridge to drive initiatives from insights through to implementation, and partner with the Stripe Finance &amp;amp; Strategy team to bring context and clarity to Bridge performance. This is a high-impact role with broad exposure across Bridge and Stripe, ideal for someone who thrives in fast-paced environments.&lt;/p&gt;
