&lt;li&gt;Ability to work cross-functionally to deliver results and build strong partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exemplary planning, prioritization, and time management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in both English and Spanish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of risk reviews, policy/compliance operations, and fraud detection tools&lt;/li&gt;
