&lt;li&gt;Work side-by-side with user-facing teams to understand their needs, develop short- and long-term solutions, and deploy those solutions across global, around-the-clock operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve internal tools that empower user-facing teams to create new workflows, publish dynamic and localized content, and respond to requests with the right context for any user.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own problems end to end: manage complexity, engage directly with stakeholders, and consider business impact, reliability and operability, and the user experience of individual interactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uphold high standards for engineering and product quality and mentor newer team members to do the same.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design clear, reusable abstractions and interfaces that other engineers can easily integrate with.&lt;/li&gt;
