&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s Degree in a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills and a structured approach to solving unique business problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with large data sets (e.g., advanced SQL and Excel skills)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An enthusiastic &quot;roll up your sleeves&quot; mentality&lt;/li&gt;
