&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of complex indirect tax planning and specialized operational projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Stripe’s expansion internationally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and interpret policy matters affecting indirect taxes internationally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the international indirect tax compliance leads, and the international accounting teams on VAT/GST compliance, to support and refine the ongoing enhancement of indirect tax compliance processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and co-ordinate indirect tax audits and other indirect tax matters involving tax authorities internationally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead interactions with other tax team members and product and engineering teams to help define indirect tax requirements and collaborate on the design of tax solutions for our users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively promote indirect tax awareness and knowledge including training and liaising with business and tax partners on changes to indirect tax legislation, systems, policies and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
