&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4 years + experience in a Software Engineering / Integration Engineering role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to write code (in programming languages like Go, Java, C/C++ etc.) and quickly debug user code snippets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with various code-level debugging (Stripe code and user code) and using code as a tool for problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;
