&lt;li&gt;Enjoy the puzzle of solving open-ended problems, both individually and as a member of our team.&lt;br&gt;Willingness to learn and teach others, including mentoring newer team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative, communicative, consultative; able to apply specific methodologies to ensure repeatability of engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
