&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills with a passion for interpreting data to improve decision-making and outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
