&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience crafting and executing SEO strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivated self-starter with high attention to detail, strong follow-through, and the ability to problem-solve independently and carry out tasks with autonomy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tech savvy and cognizant of developments in technology/fintech.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in researching and interpreting search queries for developer audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic experience with HTML, CSS, and other web programming acumens.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in all disciplines of SEO, including technical, on-site, and off-site SEO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to develop and prioritize content roadmaps to build net new pages that drive incremental business performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data-driven, and results-oriented leader that’s proficient in B2B and SEO performance data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of building scalable systems to successfully execute SEO plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in IA and site architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to develop exhaustive creative briefs for cross-functional execution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication, presentation, and soft skills (written and verbal) to effectively evangelize and educate on SEO internally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong cross-functional collaborator with the ability to build relationships and simplify complex topics for partners. Must possess intermediate sensibilities in user-experience, design, engineering, copywriting, conversion rate optimization, data, product management, and marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to develop and prioritize roadmaps that successfully deliver on business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent international SEO skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience creating performance reporting and measuring success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work extensively in Google Drive apps (Docs, Sheets, Slides), Excel, Looker, Tableau, Google Analytics and other reporting software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing stakeholders, with the ability to handle multiple work streams and requests from a variety of stakeholders, balancing each of them to deliver on the true north objectives of the channel and business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong experience using a variety of SEO tools, including Google Search Console, Google Keyword Planner, SEMRush, and ScreamingFrog.&lt;/li&gt;
