&lt;li&gt;Scope, design, build, and maintain APIs, user experiences, services, and large-scale systems that reliably and efficiently handle billions of money movement requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Debug and solve critical production issues across services and multiple levels of the stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor engineers to help them grow.&lt;/li&gt;
