&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Job Type: Full Time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: 383 Kent Street,&amp;nbsp;Sydney, NSW, 2000,&amp;nbsp;Australia&lt;/li&gt;
