&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 6+ years of experience with Fraud operations, Fraud strategy , Financial crime operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide your team in performing reviews to protect and advance Stripe’s business, brand and mission, by deploying industry-leading supportability solutions that instill user and partner trust in Stripe&lt;/li&gt;
