&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to engage in business-level and technical conversations at multiple levels of the organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
