&lt;li&gt;Lead independent discussions with TechOps, Engineering and XFN Partners to unblock complex reconciliation issues.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure your team has strong data analysis and Technical skills needed to be successful in their role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Setting clear goals and expectations for individual and team performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of continuous improvement to refine team processes and procedures.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support recruitment and hiring initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and mentor individuals to meet career via structured career development conversations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide continuous performance feedback and facilitate periodic formal performance reviews.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive and own initiatives that make the team a warm and welcoming place to work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep the team engaged and motivated towards their work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
