&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for an experienced engineer to join us and help lead Stripe&#39;s Detection Engineering Team. This team is responsible for building security analytics, threat hunting, creating detections as code, and investigating, responding and providing awareness to potential security concerns. Rather than traditional commercial tooling, you’ll help to drive codified processes, data analytics and automation for detection and response at scale. You’ll maintain strong partnerships with product and other engineering teams to help convey threat awareness and to collect requirements for any monitoring and response needs throughout Stripe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
